item.title: The Making of this Tableau Dashboard
item.description: Available at my Tableau Public: https://public.tableau.com/profile/dylan.deppiesse My first “real” project in terms of finding a dataset and turning it into something. This is something I’ve been saying I’ll do for a while and I finally forced myself to just start and see where it goes. Regardless of what the outcome was, I simply knew that starting 1 project would lead to working on more and improving as I went.
